      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>AstraZeneca</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to determine if Iressa added to chemotherapy with Irinotecan,
      5Fluorouracil and Leucovorin can prolong the period of time without any disease worsening
      (Time to Progression) in patients with metastatic colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
